{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":763,"text":"I want you all to think"},{"time":4603,"text":"about the third word\nthat was ever said about you --"},{"time":11582,"text":"or, if you were delivering,"},{"time":14638,"text":"about the person you were delivering."},{"time":19864,"text":"And you can all mouth it\nif you want or say it out loud."},{"time":23729,"text":"It was -- the first two were, \"It's a ...\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":29310,"text":"Audience: (Mixed reply) Girl. Boy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31355,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":32380,"text":"Well, it shows you that --"},{"time":34006,"text":"I also deal with issues\nwhere there's not certainty"},{"time":37109,"text":"of whether it's a girl or a boy,"},{"time":38708,"text":"so the mixed answer was very appropriate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42336,"text":"Of course, now the answer often comes\nnot at birth but at the ultrasound,"},{"time":46994,"text":"unless the prospective parents\nchoose to be surprised,"},{"time":50972,"text":"like we all were."}]},{"cues":[{"time":53835,"text":"But I want you to think about what it is\nthat leads to that statement"},{"time":60859,"text":"on the third word,"},{"time":62899,"text":"because the third word"},{"time":65400,"text":"is a description of your sex."},{"time":73159,"text":"And by that I mean,"},{"time":75572,"text":"made by a description of your genitals."},{"time":80436,"text":"Now, as a pediatric endocrinologist,"},{"time":83504,"text":"I used to be very, very involved\nand still somewhat am, in cases"},{"time":89005,"text":"in which there are mismatches\nin the externals"},{"time":95293,"text":"or between the externals\nand the internals,"},{"time":99331,"text":"and we literally have to figure out"},{"time":104168,"text":"what is the description of your sex."},{"time":108502,"text":"But there is nothing\nthat is definable at the time of birth"},{"time":113808,"text":"that would define you."},{"time":118101,"text":"And when I talk about definition,"},{"time":120268,"text":"I'm talking about your sexual orientation."},{"time":126274,"text":"We don't say, \"It's a ... gay boy!\""},{"time":131668,"text":"\"A lesbian girl!\""},{"time":134449,"text":"Those situations don't\nreally define themselves"},{"time":137982,"text":"more until the second decade of life."},{"time":141971,"text":"Nor do they define your gender,"},{"time":146952,"text":"which, as different\nfrom your anatomic sex,"},{"time":150564,"text":"describes your self-concept:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":153838,"text":"Do you see yourself as a male or female,"},{"time":159370,"text":"or somewhere in the spectrum in between?"},{"time":164593,"text":"That sometimes shows up"},{"time":169896,"text":"in the first decade of life,"},{"time":172880,"text":"but it can be very confusing for parents,"},{"time":176526,"text":"because it is quite normative for children"},{"time":181257,"text":"to act in a cross-gender play and way,"},{"time":185634,"text":"and, in fact, there are studies that show"},{"time":187968,"text":"that even 80 percent of children\nwho act in that fashion"},{"time":193820,"text":"will not persist in wanting\nto be the opposite gender"},{"time":200762,"text":"at the time when puberty begins."}]},{"cues":[{"time":204746,"text":"But, at the time that puberty begins --"},{"time":210206,"text":"that means between about age 10 to 12\nin girls, 12 to 14 in boys --"},{"time":217239,"text":"with breast budding,"},{"time":218970,"text":"or two to three times'\nincrease in the gonads"},{"time":222867,"text":"in the case of genetic males,"},{"time":225736,"text":"by that particular point,"},{"time":227386,"text":"the child who says\nthey are in the absolute wrong body"},{"time":233504,"text":"is almost certain to be transgender"},{"time":237291,"text":"and is extremely unlikely\nto change those feelings,"},{"time":244303,"text":"no matter how anybody tries\nreparative therapy"},{"time":248862,"text":"or any other noxious things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252742,"text":"Now, this is relatively rare,"},{"time":255213,"text":"so I had relatively little\npersonal experience with this."},{"time":258929,"text":"And my experience was more typical,"},{"time":261607,"text":"only because I had an adolescent practice."},{"time":263671,"text":"And I saw someone age 24,"},{"time":265363,"text":"genetically female, went through Harvard\nwith three male roommates"},{"time":269954,"text":"who knew the whole story,"},{"time":271314,"text":"a registrar who always listed his name\non course lists as a male name,"},{"time":277355,"text":"and came to me after graduating,"},{"time":280330,"text":"saying, \"Help me. I know you know\na lot of endocrinology.\""},{"time":284348,"text":"And indeed, I've treated a lot of people\nwho were born without gonads."},{"time":287680,"text":"This wasn't rocket science."},{"time":289348,"text":"But I made a deal with him:"},{"time":290975,"text":"\"I'll treat you if you teach me.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":293900,"text":"And so he did."},{"time":297161,"text":"And what an education I got"},{"time":298995,"text":"from taking care of all the members\nof his support group."},{"time":303647,"text":"And then I got really confused,"},{"time":306194,"text":"because I thought it was\nrelatively easy at that age"},{"time":308751,"text":"to just give people the hormones"},{"time":310358,"text":"of the gender\nin which they were affirming."},{"time":314595,"text":"But then my patient married,"},{"time":317825,"text":"and he married a woman\nwho had been born as a male,"},{"time":322655,"text":"had married as a male, had two children,"},{"time":325958,"text":"then went through\na transition into female."},{"time":331721,"text":"And now this delightful female"},{"time":336536,"text":"was attached to my male patient --\nin fact, got legally married,"},{"time":342226,"text":"because they showed up as a man\nand a woman, and who knew, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":345502,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":347966,"text":"And I was confused --"},{"time":351501,"text":"\"Does this make so-and-so gay?"},{"time":353922,"text":"Does this make so-and-so straight?\""},{"time":355696,"text":"I was getting sexual orientation\nconfused with gender identity."},{"time":361609,"text":"And my patient said to me,"},{"time":363808,"text":"\"Look, look, look."},{"time":365300,"text":"If you just think of the following,\nyou'll get it right:"},{"time":368737,"text":"Sexual orientation\nis who you go to bed with."},{"time":372004,"text":"Gender identity is who you go to bed as.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":375802,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":377827,"text":"And I subsequently learned\nfrom the many adults --"},{"time":380643,"text":"I took care of about 200 adults --"},{"time":383189,"text":"I learned from them"},{"time":384883,"text":"that if I didn't peek as to who\ntheir partner was in the waiting room,"},{"time":389542,"text":"I would never be able to guess\nbetter than chance,"},{"time":393241,"text":"whether they were gay,\nstraight, bi or asexual"},{"time":397463,"text":"in their affirmed gender."},{"time":399631,"text":"In other words,"},{"time":400877,"text":"one thing has absolutely nothing\nto do with the other."},{"time":405460,"text":"And the data show it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":410075,"text":"Now, as I took care of the 200 adults,"},{"time":412248,"text":"I found it extremely painful."},{"time":414814,"text":"These people -- many of them --"},{"time":417821,"text":"had to give up so much of their lives."},{"time":422122,"text":"Sometimes their parents would reject them,"},{"time":424577,"text":"siblings, their own children,"},{"time":426950,"text":"and then their divorcing spouse"},{"time":428721,"text":"would forbid them\nfrom seeing their children."},{"time":432724,"text":"It was so awful,"},{"time":434509,"text":"but why did they do it at 40 and 50?"},{"time":438289,"text":"Because they felt\nthey had to affirm themselves"},{"time":443058,"text":"before they would kill themselves."},{"time":445316,"text":"And indeed, the rate of suicide\namong untreated transgendered people"},{"time":451286,"text":"is among the highest in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":455057,"text":"So, what to do?"},{"time":457020,"text":"I was intrigued, in going\nto a conference in Holland,"},{"time":460956,"text":"where they are experts in this,"},{"time":463226,"text":"and saw the most remarkable thing."},{"time":466623,"text":"They were treating young adolescents"},{"time":469869,"text":"after giving them the most intense\npsychometric testing of gender,"},{"time":475863,"text":"and they were treating them by blocking\nthe puberty that they didn't want."},{"time":480283,"text":"Because basically,\nkids look about the same,"},{"time":482869,"text":"each sex, until they go through puberty,"},{"time":485888,"text":"at which point, if you feel\nyou're in the wrong sex,"},{"time":488605,"text":"you feel like Pinocchio becoming a donkey."},{"time":491675,"text":"The fantasy that you had\nthat your body will change"},{"time":494240,"text":"to be who you want it to be, with puberty,"},{"time":496915,"text":"actually is nullified\nby the puberty you get."},{"time":501779,"text":"And they fall apart."}]},{"cues":[{"time":505328,"text":"So that's why putting the puberty\non hold -- why on hold?"},{"time":508828,"text":"You can't just give them\nthe opposite hormones that young."},{"time":511902,"text":"They'll end up stunted in growth,"},{"time":513761,"text":"and you think you can have\na meaningful conversation"},{"time":516333,"text":"about the fertility effects\nof such treatment"},{"time":518847,"text":"with a 10-year-old girl,\na 12-year-old boy?"},{"time":522663,"text":"So this buys time\nin the diagnostic process"},{"time":525193,"text":"for four or five years,"},{"time":527045,"text":"so that they can work it out."},{"time":529819,"text":"They can have more and more testing,"},{"time":532471,"text":"they can live without feeling their bodies\nare running away from them."},{"time":536464,"text":"And then, in a program they call 12-16-18,"},{"time":540646,"text":"around age 12 is when they\ngive the blocking hormones,"},{"time":545519,"text":"and then at age 16, with retesting,"},{"time":547983,"text":"they re-qualify to receive --"},{"time":550289,"text":"now remember, the blocking\nhormones are reversible,"},{"time":553285,"text":"but when you give the hormones\nof the opposite sex,"},{"time":556190,"text":"you now start spouting breasts\nand facial hair and voice change,"},{"time":559531,"text":"depending on what you're using,"},{"time":561297,"text":"and those effects are permanent,"},{"time":563423,"text":"or require surgery to remove,"},{"time":565265,"text":"or electrolysis,"},{"time":566520,"text":"and you can never really affect the voice."},{"time":569027,"text":"So this is serious,\nand this is 15-, 16-year-old stuff."}]},{"cues":[{"time":573184,"text":"And then at 18,\nthey're eligible for surgery."},{"time":576772,"text":"And while there's no good surgery\nfor females to males genitally,"},{"time":580888,"text":"the male-to-female surgery\nhas fooled gynecologists."},{"time":585381,"text":"That's how good it can be."},{"time":588087,"text":"So I looked at how\nthe patients were doing,"},{"time":592088,"text":"and I looked at patients\nwho just looked like everybody else,"},{"time":594974,"text":"except they were pubertally delayed."},{"time":597729,"text":"But once they gave them the hormones"},{"time":599666,"text":"consistent with the gender they affirm,"},{"time":602299,"text":"they look beautiful."},{"time":604229,"text":"They look normal."},{"time":606040,"text":"They had normal heights."},{"time":607935,"text":"You would never be able\nto pick them out in a crowd."}]},{"cues":[{"time":612522,"text":"So at that point, I decided\nI'm going to do this."},{"time":615103,"text":"This is really where the pediatric\nendocrine realm comes in,"},{"time":619611,"text":"because, in fact, if you're going to deal\nwith it in kids aged 10 to 14,"},{"time":624452,"text":"that's pediatric endocrinology."},{"time":627354,"text":"So I brought some kids in,"},{"time":631513,"text":"and this now became the standard of care,"},{"time":634098,"text":"and the [Boston]\nChildren's Hospital was behind it."},{"time":636927,"text":"By my showing them\nthe kids before and after,"},{"time":641094,"text":"people who never got treated\nand people who wished to be treated,"},{"time":644939,"text":"and pictures of the Dutch --"},{"time":648035,"text":"they came to me and said,"},{"time":649280,"text":"\"You've got to do\nsomething for these kids.\""},{"time":651511,"text":"Well, where were these kids before?"},{"time":654774,"text":"They were out there suffering,\nis where they were."}]},{"cues":[{"time":657894,"text":"So we started a program in 2007."},{"time":664062,"text":"It became the first program of its kind --"},{"time":666482,"text":"but it's really of the Dutch kind --"},{"time":668863,"text":"in North America."},{"time":670927,"text":"And since then, we have 160 patients."},{"time":675180,"text":"Did they come from Afghanistan? No."},{"time":678440,"text":"75 percent of them came\nfrom within 150 miles of Boston."}]},{"cues":[{"time":686701,"text":"And some came from England."},{"time":690138,"text":"Jackie had been abused\nin the Midlands, in England."},{"time":694205,"text":"She's 12 years old there,"},{"time":696091,"text":"she was living as a girl,"},{"time":697428,"text":"but she was being beaten up."},{"time":699610,"text":"It was a horror show,\nthey had to homeschool her."},{"time":702649,"text":"And the reason the British were coming"},{"time":705017,"text":"was because they would not treat\nanybody with anything under age 16,"},{"time":710741,"text":"which means they were consigning\nthem to an adult body"},{"time":714478,"text":"no matter what happened,"},{"time":715961,"text":"even if they tested them well."},{"time":718108,"text":"Jackie, on top of it, was,\nby virtue of skeletal markings,"},{"time":722810,"text":"destined to be six feet five."},{"time":727138,"text":"And yet, she had just begun\na male puberty."}]},{"cues":[{"time":730938,"text":"Well, I did something\na little bit innovative,"},{"time":734537,"text":"because I do know hormones,"},{"time":736659,"text":"and that estrogen is much more potent"},{"time":738621,"text":"in closing epiphyses, the growth plates,"},{"time":742435,"text":"and stopping growth, than testosterone is."},{"time":745752,"text":"So we blocked her testosterone\nwith a blocking hormone,"},{"time":750505,"text":"but we added estrogen,\nnot at 16, but at 13."},{"time":754909,"text":"And so here she is at 16, on the left."},{"time":758093,"text":"And on her 16th birthday,\nshe went to Thailand,"},{"time":760395,"text":"where they would do\na genital plastic surgery."},{"time":762697,"text":"They will do it at 18 now."},{"time":764597,"text":"And she ended up 5'11\"."},{"time":767312,"text":"But more than that,\nshe has normal breast size,"},{"time":770559,"text":"because by blocking testosterone,"},{"time":772871,"text":"every one of our patients\nhas normal breast size"},{"time":776249,"text":"if they get to us at the appropriate age,"},{"time":779283,"text":"not too late."}]},{"cues":[{"time":781057,"text":"And on the far right, there she is."},{"time":782840,"text":"She went public -- semifinalist\nin the Miss England competition."},{"time":789068,"text":"The judges debated\nas to, can they do this?"},{"time":792134,"text":"And one of them quipped, I'm told,"},{"time":796309,"text":"\"But she has more natural self\nthan half the other contestants.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":800299,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":802211,"text":"And some of them\nhave been rearranged a little bit,"},{"time":806482,"text":"but it's all her DNA."},{"time":809679,"text":"And she's become a remarkable spokeswoman."},{"time":813121,"text":"And she was offered contracts as a model,"},{"time":817006,"text":"at which point\nshe teased me, when she said,"},{"time":819155,"text":"\"You know, I might have had\na better chance as a model"},{"time":821724,"text":"if you'd made me six feet one.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":823456,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":825460,"text":"Go figure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":828038,"text":"So this picture, I think, says it all."},{"time":831740,"text":"It really says it all."},{"time":833760,"text":"These are Nicole and brother Jonas,"},{"time":837408,"text":"identical twin boys,"},{"time":840427,"text":"and proven to be identical."},{"time":843978,"text":"Nicole had affirmed herself\nas a girl as early as age three."},{"time":847596,"text":"At age seven, they changed her name,"},{"time":850127,"text":"and came to me at the very\nbeginnings of a male puberty."},{"time":854904,"text":"Now you can imagine\nlooking at Jonas at only 14,"},{"time":857712,"text":"that male puberty is early in this family,"},{"time":860523,"text":"because he looks more like a 16-year-old."},{"time":863086,"text":"But it makes the point all the more,"},{"time":864920,"text":"of why you have to be conscious\nof where the patient is."},{"time":868665,"text":"Nicole is on pubertal blockade in here,"},{"time":872451,"text":"and Jonas is just going --\nbiologic control."},{"time":876189,"text":"This is what Nicole would look like"},{"time":877910,"text":"if we weren't doing what we were doing."},{"time":879991,"text":"He's got a prominent Adam's apple."},{"time":882482,"text":"He's got angular bones\nto the face, a mustache,"},{"time":886063,"text":"and you can see there's\na height difference,"},{"time":888150,"text":"because he's gone through\na growth spurt that she won't get."},{"time":891053,"text":"Now Nicole is on estrogen."},{"time":892594,"text":"She has a bit of a form to her."}]},{"cues":[{"time":895887,"text":"This family went\nto the White House last spring,"},{"time":899526,"text":"because of their work in overturning\nan anti-discrimination --"},{"time":905289,"text":"there was a bill that would block"},{"time":907695,"text":"the right of transgender people in Maine\nto use public bathrooms,"},{"time":912322,"text":"and it looked like the bill\nwas going to pass,"},{"time":915091,"text":"and that would have been a problem,"},{"time":916822,"text":"but Nicole went personally\nto every legislator in Maine"},{"time":920323,"text":"and said, \"I can do this."},{"time":922335,"text":"If they see me, they'll understand"},{"time":924351,"text":"why I'm no threat in the ladies' room,"},{"time":926521,"text":"but I can be threatened\nin the men's room.\""},{"time":928627,"text":"And then they finally got it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":932038,"text":"So where do we go from here?"},{"time":935022,"text":"Well, we still have a ways to go\nin terms of anti-discrimination."},{"time":939115,"text":"There are only 17 states\nthat have an anti-discrimination law"},{"time":942806,"text":"against discrimination in housing,"},{"time":945406,"text":"employment, public accommodation --"},{"time":948522,"text":"only 17 states, and five of them\nare in New England."},{"time":951534,"text":"We need less expensive drugs."},{"time":953459,"text":"They cost a fortune."},{"time":955164,"text":"And we need to get\nthis condition out of the DSM."},{"time":959081,"text":"It is as much a psychiatric disease\nas being gay and lesbian,"},{"time":963805,"text":"and that went out the window in 1973,"},{"time":966748,"text":"and the whole world changed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":968649,"text":"And this isn't going to break\nanybody's budget."},{"time":971018,"text":"This is not that common."},{"time":973279,"text":"But the risks of not\ndoing anything for them"},{"time":978005,"text":"not only puts all of them at risk\nof losing their lives to suicide,"},{"time":984501,"text":"but it also says something about\nwhether we are a truly inclusive society."}]},{"cues":[{"time":990777,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":991952,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}